# **Delivery Policy **


---

## 1. How We Deliver Services

ST² services are delivered manually by an operator.
Delivery times are **targets**, not guarantees:

| Product           | Target Delivery | Notes                            |
| ----------------- | --------------- | -------------------------------- |
| Snapshot          | ~30 minutes     | Depends on operator availability |
| Hardening         | ~1 hour         | Same as above                    |
| Mini Pentest LITE | Same day        | Usually within a few hours       |
| Mini Honeypot Kit | Instant         | Digital download                 |

---

## 2. Time Zone Policy

We operate in CET/CEST (Europe).
US & Canadian orders are processed **in their local daytime hours whenever possible**, but:

* Orders placed outside operator working hours queue for next availability
* Priority is given to orders placed 9:00–23:00 CET
* Emergency/ASAP delivery can be arranged manually

---

## 3. Honest Expectations 

> “ST² aims to deliver all services as fast as possible.
> All delivery times are targets based on typical workload.
> Because services are performed by human operators, slight delays may occur.
> You will always receive confirmation when your order begins processing.”
